		<description><![CDATA[In old age, I had to come to terms with the loneliness I’d felt all my life]]></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<img width="1200" height="1320" src="https://walrus-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/img/Butala_Loneliness_1200.jpg" class="webfeedsFeaturedVisual wp-post-image" alt="Photograph of pink flowers in a black ceramic vase on a shabby concrete floor." loading="lazy" style="display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; clear:both;max-width: 100%;" link_thumbnail="" /><h4>Listen to an audio version of this story</h4>
