<div class="special-series-body">
<h1 style="font-family: GT Sectra; padding-bottom:0.2em;"><a href="https://thewalrus.ca/our-national-silence-on-bill-21/">The Decade in Us</a></h1>
<h5 style="font-family: GT Sectra; font-weight: 200; padding-bottom: 60px;">As the 2010s come to close, we look back at a mix of your favourite stories and speakers. From building a life without kids to why shared work offices are the worst, these are the ideas, people, and conversations that helped define Canada </p>
<div class="addthis_sharing_toolbox"></div>
</h5>
